{"tid":1092144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［抄大陸卷］DSE寫作卷題目與南京中考相似   考評局認為不一樣","createTime":"2019-04-04T15:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T12:29:23.000Z","uid":20058,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"718552a520e818739b6ec76596839730ab4fbdd0","tid":1092144,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T15:24:09.000Z","msg":"【DSE寫作卷題目與南京中考相似   考評局認為不一樣】<br />\n<br />\n今年中學文憑試中文科寫作卷，有一條題目與2015年南京中考題目很相似。<br />\n<br />\n考評局指，出題人員要簽署保證書，聲明題目不是直接取用其他試題，但局方認為兩條題目不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #考評局 #中學文憑試 #中文科 #寫作 #南京中考<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1084225838436150?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1084225838436150%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=06ec560f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1084225838436150?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"c220588c8c5d431631091fdd12feb83cbdebf43e","tid":1092144,"uid":90372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T19:27:36.000Z","msg":"考評局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cc8a54cbb31df7966d406b5bd0f4dab574d860","tid":1092144,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:42:47.000Z","msg":"唔同？<br />\n<br />\n先說卷二作文。第二題是節錄了《想想別人》一詩的其中三節，以「想想別人」為題，寫出「你對這首詩歌的體會或聯想」。這條題目，看似新鮮；與以前的作文題型很不一樣。明眼人一看就知，無論語言、文化，都沒有本地的氣息。答案有了，這是 2015 年南京中考的作文題目。<br />\n<br />\n巴勒斯坦诗人达维什诗歌《想想别人》的一段话：&ldquo;当你做早餐时想想别人，别忘了喂鸽子&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo; 意思就是这个世界上，有你，有我，有他（她、它）。请以 &ldquo;想想别人&rdquo; 为题，写一篇文章。<br />\n<br />\n要求：① 除诗歌外，文体不限；② 不少于 600 个字；③ 文中不得出现真实的地名、校名和人名；④ 书写要工整、规范、美观。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.zhongkao.com/nj/e/20150613/557c0204dc45b.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.zhongkao.com%2Fnj%2Fe%2F20150613%2F557c0204dc45b.shtml&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=93cccfc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.zhongkao.com/nj/e/20150613/557c0204dc45b.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n網上對於這條題目的寫作分析，審題、運意、構思、敘事，都有詳盡的指導；甚至附有「範文」。這不是試題洩露，又是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n卷一的文言閱讀理解，亦是香港學生的致命傷。今年的篇章很短，是清人劉熙載的《海鷗與巷燕》。諸生切勿歡喜過早，以為執到。原來這篇試題，原封不動，是抄自大陸高考的練習。（見例題五<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/axkr6jn.html）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2Faxkr6jn.html%EF%BC%89&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=b94ae173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/axkr6jn.html）</a>"},{"pid":"9b7a6ba41775c0a26f205d7c9e15ac7a78e06f4f","tid":1092144,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:43:05.000Z","msg":"DSE中文科考題 原來係用咗強國考試題目！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1090681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1090681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eec93c6749a1d71c88f77c737a522525d06af2d0","tid":1092144,"uid":138267,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"開始同上面接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3571c0d6075bd61dc5c17178184b9d6765f6c1e","tid":1092144,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86550a49976530e2f7ae4a06e0b06e74ed9571d9","tid":1092144,"uid":182244,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:51:05.000Z","msg":"你用想想別人都算，連首詩都同一首喎，好難唔覺係無抄囉"},{"pid":"1f6e9802e4a587041091869ce9cd7df809d93856","tid":1092144,"uid":139700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"你班奶共狗奶得咁開心！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfcad3ad6ec702ee3d2c1dc68cb320c733a49ca","tid":1092144,"uid":39698,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201